[
  {
    "content_id": 798397,
    "reference_id": 25323,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶和華傳遞了這樣的信息：西番雅是一位先知，是神的代言人。</p></li><li><p>希西家可能指的是使用此名的王（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:1-2Kgs20:20\">王下18:1–20:20</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:1",
          "end_ref": "36001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798391,
    "reference_id": 25317,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:1–2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001001-36002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>西番亞從耶和華那裡領受的信息，不單單預警了對全地的審判（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:1-Zeph1:6\">1:1–6</a>），還勸誡讀者在災難降臨（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:14-Zeph1:18\">1:14–18</a>）之前悔改 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:7-Zeph1:13\">1:7–13</a>）、尋求耶和華，並在祂面前過公義而謙卑的生活，盼望他們能夠以此免於耶和華的審判 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:1-Zeph2:3\">2:1–3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:1",
          "end_ref": "36002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798398,
    "reference_id": 25324,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:2–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001002-36001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神將要在祂的審判中除滅的事物，是以這些事物被創造時的相反順序排列的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:26\">創1:20–26</a>）：人和牲畜……鳥……魚，因為審判是創造的逆轉。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:2",
          "end_ref": "36001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798400,
    "reference_id": 25326,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>西番雅發出這個預言時，約西亞還未在公元前622年進行改革，拜偶像的祭司猖獗地宣揚巴力崇拜和其它形式的異教信仰（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:5\">王下23:5</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:4",
          "end_ref": "36001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798399,
    "reference_id": 25325,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:4–6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001004-36001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在對全地宣告審判（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:2-Zeph1:3\">1:2–3</a>）之後，西番雅現在將注意力集中在祂自己的人民——猶大和耶路撒冷身上。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:4",
          "end_ref": "36001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798401,
    "reference_id": 25327,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>經文譴責敬拜天體如太陽、月亮和星星的行為（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15-Deut4:19\">申4:15–19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:3\">王下21:3</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:12\">23:12</a>）。</p></li><li><p>摩洛可能是指迦南神巴力、亞捫神米勒公或異教神摩洛。儘管律法明確禁止敬拜摩洛（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:5\">利20:1–5</a>），但對以色列而言，這仍是一個持續的試探（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:3\">王下16:3</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:6\">21:6</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:5",
          "end_ref": "36001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798403,
    "reference_id": 25329,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華已為祂的子民預備了一場大屠殺，並已選擇了行刑的劊子手：外邦人將<em>屠殺</em>神子民中的惡人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:7",
          "end_ref": "36001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798402,
    "reference_id": 25328,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:7–18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001007-36001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段落必須被視為一個重大的事件。事件的一部分會在耶路撒冷於公元前586年陷落時成就；其餘部分則會在不同的歷史時期重複出現（如耶路撒冷在公元70年的毀滅），直到最終神完全地審判世界並更新創造，整個預言會在末了完全成就（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11-Rev22:5\">啟19:11–22:5</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:7",
          "end_ref": "36001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798404,
    "reference_id": 25330,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>猶大的領袖和王子包括以色列的支派族長（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:4\">民1:4</a>）、宮廷官員（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:17\">代上22:17</a>）、省長（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:14-1Kgs20:15\">王上20:14–15</a>）、城市官員（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:6\">士8:6</a>）、軍事領袖（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:5\">王上2:5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:9-2Kgs1:14\">王下1:9–14</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:23\">25:23</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:26\">26</a>），甚至是宗教領袖（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:24\">拉8:24</a>）。他們的影響力使得他們在神面前承擔更大的責任（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1\">雅3:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:8",
          "end_ref": "36001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798405,
    "reference_id": 25331,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>參加異教崇拜儀式的人（字面意思是<em>那些跳過門檻的人</em>；和合本譯為：跳過門檻......的）：猶大人延續了異教的習俗，跳過神廟的門檻，避免接觸神廟，以表示對那位異教神的敬畏（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:1-1Sam5:5\">撒上5:1–5</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:9",
          "end_ref": "36001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798392,
    "reference_id": 25318,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>魚門位於耶路撒冷的北部（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:39\">尼12:39</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:10",
          "end_ref": "36001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798393,
    "reference_id": 25319,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神將差派一支侵略軍來掠奪耶路撒冷。毀滅會來得非常之快，以至於那些擁有不義之財的人將無法倖存下來享受他們的財富。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:13",
          "end_ref": "36001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798394,
    "reference_id": 25320,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:14–18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001014-36001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華的日子的意義擴展至包括了神對全地的作為。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:14",
          "end_ref": "36001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798395,
    "reference_id": 25321,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>黑暗幽冥：另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:9-Isa13:10\">賽13:9–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:1-Joel2:2\">約珥書2:1–2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:18-Amos5:20\">摩5:18–20</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:15",
          "end_ref": "36001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798396,
    "reference_id": 25322,
    "title": "西番雅書 1:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36001017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>行走如同瞎眼的：這是神公義的一個例子（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:32\">羅1:21–32</a>）。因為神的子民在道德和靈性上都是瞎眼的（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:8\">出23:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:19\">羅2:19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:11\">約一2:11</a>），並且違背了耶和華和祂的誡命，因此他們將承受神與他們所立之約中所定的公正懲罰（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28-Deut28:29\">申28:28–29</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36001017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:17",
          "end_ref": "36001017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 1:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798406,
    "reference_id": 25332,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:1–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002001-36002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>鑒於西番雅所描述的可怕景象，他呼籲他的國民悔改，並在神面前謙卑自己。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:1",
          "end_ref": "36002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798412,
    "reference_id": 25338,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>農民在多風的山頂上為農作物脱粒。當他們將混合的穀物和<span>糠秕</span>拋向空中時，風會將<span>糠秕</span>吹走，而較重的穀物則落回地面。悔改的機會稍縱即逝。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:2",
          "end_ref": "36002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798413,
    "reference_id": 25339,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>謙卑人：真正的謙卑包括順服和倚靠神 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:25-Ps18:27\">詩18:25–27</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:142-Ps119:144\">119:142–144</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">箴15:33</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:12\">18:12</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">22:4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:3",
          "end_ref": "36002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798416,
    "reference_id": 25342,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒征服了非利士的城市迦薩、亞實基倫、亞實突和以革倫。迦薩依舊荒廢，但其他城市卻復興，並延續到後來的時代。西番雅沒有提到迦特，即第五個主要的非利士城市（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:17\">撒上6:17</a>），可能是因為它在西番雅的時代已經消失或變得不再重要。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:4",
          "end_ref": "36002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798414,
    "reference_id": 25340,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:4–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002004-36002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>西番雅的宣告由非利士人開始，非利士人的王國位於猶大西邊（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:4-Zeph2:7\">2:4–7</a>）。接著，他轉向東方的摩押和亞捫（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:8-Zeph2:11\">2:8–11</a>），最後特別提到南方的古實（衣索匹亞，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:12\">2:12</a>）和北方的亞述（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:13-Zeph2:15\">2:13–15</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:4",
          "end_ref": "36002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798415,
    "reference_id": 25341,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:4–3:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002004-36003020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在回到對猶大和耶路撒冷的審判（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:1-Zeph3:8\">3:1–8</a>）之前，西番雅將注意力轉向了對外邦的審判（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:4-Zeph2:15\">2:4–15</a>）。隨後，他概述了神對其已潔淨的及順服的子民的計劃（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9-Zeph3:20\">3:9–20</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:4",
          "end_ref": "36002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798417,
    "reference_id": 25343,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>舊約聖經學者認為非利士人來自克里特島（<span>Island of Crete，</span>參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:16\">結25:16</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:5",
          "end_ref": "36002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798418,
    "reference_id": 25344,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>草場......牧人的住處和羊群的圈：城市的毀滅及其恢復自然狀態代表來自神的嚴厲懲罰。另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:23-Isa7:25\">以賽亞書七章23至25節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19-Isa13:21\">十三章19至21節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:9-Isa32:15\">三十二章9至15節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek35:9\">以西結書三十五章9節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:6",
          "end_ref": "36002006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798419,
    "reference_id": 25345,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>敬拜巴力者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:4\">1:4</a>）和非利士人將永遠不會被復興（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:4-Zeph2:6\">2:4–6</a>；另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:8\">摩1:8</a>）。相比之下，神卻應許將祂的餘民帶回他們的土地、牧養他們，並恢復他們至興旺（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:18-Zeph3:20\">番3:18–20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:11-Isa11:16\">賽11:11–16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:1-Jer23:8\">耶23:1–8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:16\">結34:11–16</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:20-Ezek34:31\">20–31</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:7",
          "end_ref": "36002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798420,
    "reference_id": 25346,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>摩押人和亞捫人是以色列的傳統仇敵。以色列人經常與他們交戰（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:1-2Kgs3:27\">王下3:1–27</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:1-2Chr20:30\">代下20:1–30</a>），直到最後他們也仍是以色列的敵人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:25\">王下25:25</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:11-Jer40:14\">耶40:11–14</a>）。</p></li><li><p>毀謗......侵犯：以色列人不僅要承受摩押人和亞捫人的反覆攻擊（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">摩1:13</a>），還要忍受這些人勝利後對他們發出的羞辱。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:8",
          "end_ref": "36002008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798421,
    "reference_id": 25347,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>所多瑪和蛾摩拉的毀滅是神嚴厲審判罪的例子，無論是在舊約聖經中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:23\">申29:23</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:9\">賽1:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:14\">耶23:14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:11\">摩4:11</a>）還是在新約聖經中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:12\">路10:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:29\">羅9:29</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:6\">彼後2:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>鹽坑：一片荒蕪的廢墟（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:23\">申29:23</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:34\">詩107:34</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:6\">耶17:6</a>）。用鹽撒地是永久審判的標記（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:45\">士9:45</a>），因為它會使土地貧瘠。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:9",
          "end_ref": "36002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798407,
    "reference_id": 25333,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>列國海島的居民......敬拜他：在歷史的末了，一切地方的所有人都將單單敬拜神（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9\">3:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:4\">詩66:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:1-Mic4:2\">彌4:1–2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">亞14:16</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:11",
          "end_ref": "36002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798408,
    "reference_id": 25334,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>古實人：希伯來文為<em>Cushites。</em> 雖然這個希伯來用語可以指當時已知世界南部邊緣的任何國家或民族，但在此特指統治埃及的衣索匹亞王朝（Ethiopian dynasty）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:12",
          "end_ref": "36002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798409,
    "reference_id": 25335,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>西番雅從南方（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:12\">2:12</a>）轉向了北方。如同在他之前的那鴻一樣，他宣告了亞述即將滅亡。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:13",
          "end_ref": "36002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798410,
    "reference_id": 25336,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>為了強調他對尼尼微的結局的看法，西番雅引用了強而有力的意象：瓦礫將填滿曾經是尼尼微富人和權貴行走的門口。<span>空窗中貓頭鷹怪誕的鳴叫聲，</span>將點綴這座城市的荒涼。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:14",
          "end_ref": "36002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798411,
    "reference_id": 25337,
    "title": "西番雅書 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>荒涼：毀滅是如此確定且不可逆轉（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:14\">鴻1:14</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:13\">2:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:19\">3:19</a>），以至於西番雅看不到亞述或其首都的未來。尼尼微的毀滅是如此徹底，以至於希臘歷史學家色諾芬（<span>Xenophon</span>）曾經過其廢墟而不知其存在。</p></li><li><p>搖手嗤笑：那些在亞述殘暴帝國下受苦的人會很高興看到它的滅亡。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:15",
          "end_ref": "36002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798431,
    "reference_id": 25357,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>被污穢的耶路撒冷已經遠離了其應成為聖城的呼召 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:1\">賽52:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:1",
          "end_ref": "36003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798422,
    "reference_id": 25348,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:1–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003001-36003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>西番雅對猶大和耶路撒冷宣告了一條悲哀的信息，並告誡他們要耐心等待神公義審判的結果。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:1",
          "end_ref": "36003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798433,
    "reference_id": 25359,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:3–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003003-36003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:23-Ezek22:29\">以西結書二十二章23至29節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:3",
          "end_ref": "36003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798434,
    "reference_id": 25360,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>祂沒有做錯什麼，不像<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:3-Zeph3:4\">三章3至4節</a>中所提到的那些人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:5",
          "end_ref": "36003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798435,
    "reference_id": 25361,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>從早起來：耶路撒冷的市民一大早便迫不及待地跳下床，去做更多的惡事（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:16\">箴1:16</a>）。他們已經遠離了他們祖先亞伯拉罕的道路，亞伯拉罕是早起去遵行神的命令（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:3\">創22:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:7",
          "end_ref": "36003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798436,
    "reference_id": 25362,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>要等候：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">哈巴谷書二章3節</a>。</p></li><li><p>興起擄掠：先知描繪了一個法庭場景，其中神首先作為證人出現（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:23\">耶29:23</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">瑪3:5</a>）為自己作證，然後作為法官主持（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:15\">伯9:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:6\">詩50:6</a>），以宣告祂的公義判決。</p></li><li><p>我的嫉妒之火（和合本譯為：忿怒如火）描述了耶和華對罪公義的憎恨、對自己聖名的擔憂和對子民福祉的關心（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:13-Isa66:16\">賽66:13–16</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:8",
          "end_ref": "36003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798439,
    "reference_id": 25365,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神盼望在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9-Zeph3:13\">三章9至13節</a>中所應許給忠信餘民的祝福能夠傳遞給世界各國的人。使得不僅是以色列，而是所有人都被改變，開始尋求耶和華（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:5\">賽55:5</a>）並服事祂（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:19-Isa59:21\">賽59:19–21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">亞14:16</a>）。好消息傳向萬國是此異象進一步的成就（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">太28:19–20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:13\">羅10:9–13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:9",
          "end_ref": "36003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798437,
    "reference_id": 25363,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:9–13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003009-36003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這些經文所描述的榮耀未來進一步提供了耐心等待耶和華的理由（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">3:8</a>）。如同其它先知書——以賽亞書、那鴻書和哈巴谷書——一樣，西番雅書以審判和盼望為雙重主題。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:9",
          "end_ref": "36003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798438,
    "reference_id": 25364,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:9–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003009-36003020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神啟示了祂對祂子民中謙卑而潔淨的餘民的計劃（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9-Zeph3:13\">3:9–13</a>），並鼓勵他們因即將到來的豐盛祝福和施行拯救的耶和華而歡喜快樂（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:14-Zeph3:20\">3:14–20</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:9",
          "end_ref": "36003020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798423,
    "reference_id": 25349,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>古實河是尼羅河的遙遠源頭。古代世界認為尼羅河的起源是一個巨大的謎團，因此這種說法是在指地球上最遙遠的地方。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:10",
          "end_ref": "36003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798424,
    "reference_id": 25350,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彌賽亞耶穌完美地表現出預言中所描述的以色列敬虔餘民的道德品質（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:4\">賽42:1–4</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">53:3</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:9\">7–9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">亞9:9</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">太11:28–30</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:15-Matt12:21\">12:15–21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:8\">腓2:1–8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">彼前2:23</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:12",
          "end_ref": "36003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798425,
    "reference_id": 25351,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>歌唱……歡呼……！應當滿心歡喜快樂：這些疊加的命令，強調了神的子民有一天將會體驗到無比的喜樂。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:14",
          "end_ref": "36003014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798426,
    "reference_id": 25352,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>真正的以色列王一直是耶和華（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:21\">民23:21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:7\">撒上8:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:6\">賽44:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>在你中間：另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:4-Isa54:8\">以賽亞書五十四章4至8節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:14-Isa57:19\">五十七章14至19節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:10-Isa62:12\">六十二章10至12節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek48:35\">以西結書四十八章35節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:17\">約珥書三章17節</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:21\">21節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:15",
          "end_ref": "36003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798427,
    "reference_id": 25353,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>施行拯救、大有能力的耶和華：耶和華是以色列的<span>神</span>聖<span>戰士</span>和救贖者（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:8-Ps24:10\">詩24:8–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:13\">賽42:13</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:8-Hab3:15\">哈3:8–15</a>）。神的稱號之一是「全能的神」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:21\">賽10:21</a>）。這個稱號也適用於彌賽亞（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">賽9:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>他......必因你歡欣喜樂：不僅耶路撒冷和所有以色列民會因神<em>喜樂</em>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:14\">番3:14</a>），神也將因他們純潔且忠心而喜樂（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:12-Zeph3:13\">3:12–13</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:17",
          "end_ref": "36003017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798429,
    "reference_id": 25355,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我必聚集他們……不再蒙羞（和合本譯為：因你擔當羞辱的，我必聚集他們）：耶和華的保證與書卷的開頭形成鮮明對比，那時神威脅要聚集列國將猶大人民從地面上除滅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:2-Zeph1:4\">1:2–4</a>），然而現在祂承諾要聚集那些被趕出耶路撒冷的人，並安全地帶他們歸家。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "36003018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:18",
          "end_ref": "36003018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "ZEP 3:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798428,
    "reference_id": 25354,
    "title": "西番雅書 3:18–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "36003018-36003020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>這幾節經文中反覆出現的「我必」，強調了神對祂子民進一步的保證。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
